com.readytalk.swt.text.tokenizer

Class TextToken

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.readytalk.swt.text.tokenizer.TextToken

  • public class TextToken
extends java.lang.Object
    TextToken represents a section of contiguous text that shares a common styling as specified by the TextType contained within.
